txt.en: 'Weeding is never fun, but if we all work together we can clear our walk of weeds and keep our village pristine and beautiful. What say you? Will you pitch in?'
When neighbours work together, the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads will shine as bright as the beacons.
Weeds can be found in the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads.\n\nYou should pull up weeds.
